title: The Strongest Golden Kidney System
description: Description : Cangyan Continent, where strong is respected! Alchemy is the best! The law is only a tool to restrain mortals, and among the strong, only the rules established by strength will be recognized. The almost primitive law of the jungle is the true status quo of Cangyan Continent. In this context, it tells the story of Ye Yun, a teenager who sold kidneys and bought iPhone, once traveled to the world of cultivation in Cangyan Continent. The alchemy master of Cangyan Continent was respected, and Ye Yun was forced to practice the skills of becoming a woman by his second uncle Fa, but had no choice but to save oneself and seize the position of Patriarch! Until he found out that his kidneys could not only make alchemy but also had the function of a smartphone, everything changed…
